[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "ほら、着いたぞ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ユーディー",
		"romanized_name": "Judie",
		"model_path_hash": "2697025160672431728",
		"text": "わあ……相変わらずここは寂れてるなあ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2032894617718182411",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "あれ、あそこに居るの、アーシャじゃない？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "あ、みんな。こんにちは。なにしてるの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "そっちこそこんな所でなにしてるの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "アーシャは薬士として、\n前からここの連中の面倒を見てるんだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "そういえばあんた、前はここに住んでたわよね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "ああ。ここの連中にはとても世話になった。\n今でも感謝してるよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "だから、こうしてたまに食いモンを配ってるんだ。\n貧しくて生活が厳しい奴らがたくさん居るからな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ユーディー",
		"romanized_name": "Judie",
		"model_path_hash": "2697025160672431728",
		"text": "どうしてそこまで……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2032894617718182411",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "……俺が船も妻も失って、生きる意味を見失ってた時、\n受け入れてくれたのがここの連中だ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "自分たちだって苦しいのによ。それでも\n助けてくれたんだ。その恩に報いたいってだけさ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "よし、それじゃあ配るぞ。お前らも手伝え！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "はーい！　えっと、向こうのおばあちゃんに……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ユーディー",
		"romanized_name": "Judie",
		"model_path_hash": "2697025160672431728",
		"text": "こんにちは。ご飯、持ってきましたよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2032894617718182411",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "おじさん、これどうぞ。\nあったかいうちに食べてね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "よし、これで全部だな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "みんなのおかげで助かったよ……あ、そうだ、\nそろそろキースさんに宝石パイプの替えを渡さないと",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "宝石パイプ？　また新しいの作ったの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "うん。前の薬草パイプよりもっと健康に良くて、\n火も使わないし煙も出ない特注品なんだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "まだまだ旅したいって言ってるから、\n健康には気を遣ってあげないと",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ユーディー",
		"romanized_name": "Judie",
		"model_path_hash": "2697025160672431728",
		"text": "アーシャ、優しいね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2032894617718182411",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "えへへ、わたし、薬士だからね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "ねえアーシャさん、そのパイプ、\nあたしがキースさんに届けてあげるよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "ほんと？　助かるなあ。\nじゃあお願いしてもいいかな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "任せて！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ふふふ、これでイタズラの名案が浮かんだよ！）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]